Interface CrudService<T,U>

All Known Subinterfaces:
CarService, ComponentService
All Known Implementing Classes:
CarServiceImpl, ComponentServiceImpl, CrudServiceGeneric
public interface CrudService<T,U>
The CrudService interface provides the basic CRUD (Create, Read, Update, Delete) operations for any entity type T with the identifier type U.

This interface defines standard methods for interacting with entities, such as finding, deleting, and retrieving lists of entities by their IDs.
